gramming languages.</p></div><div class="card !p-4"><span class="font-semibold text-ink">GitHub Copilot</span><p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted">An AI pair programmer that provides autocomplete suggestions, interactive chat support, and codebase search within major IDEs.</p></div><div class="card !p-4"><span class="font-semibold text-ink">Windsurf</span><p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted">An AI-powered development environment built on a flow state model that merges agentic capabilities with developer editor interactions.</p></div></div>
